{"type": "article", "id": 28652, "title": "汽水包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-24T06:50:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607031210278HnRWlDO3eGCyabf.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>Dalston 是英国伦敦的一家汽水公司，近日委托了 <a href=\"http://www.bandb-studio.co.uk/\">B&amp;B studio</a> 设计一套强调品牌主张的包装。设计师们在包装上保留了“伦敦制造”以及“手工捣碎”这两句标语，并且巧妙地将捣碎动作组成品牌的首字母 D 与不同的原料对应，既直观又很有趣。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121025x4c1i2wfRepA95jT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74933333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031210265Cx9Tg64l2eKn7rd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61066667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121027YLZryviUFDKwx1J0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.84\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}